Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.73,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I've never had to move before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:30.05,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Dad said he wanted to open his own studio away from the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:32.54,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,so we ended up leaving Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.62,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I had to change schools, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:40.80,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I hope I'll be able to manage in a completely new environment.
Comment: 0,0:01:18.97,0:02:49.02,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:53.77,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's so cold—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.46,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.36,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.08,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.37,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:03.45,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.70,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.58,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Okay, it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:16.61,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wow, it's the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.80,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,My name's Fukami Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.18,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'm Okikura Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:28.32,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Thank you again for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.05,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,The fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:29.85,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.27,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You're here for the fireworks, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:35.55,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It's not that bad at the moment, \Nbut there'll be a lot more people—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I just moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:36.98,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,There's a fireworks display today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:40.73,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.38,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:46.12,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,On the right side of the harbor, \Nthere's a beach and a breakwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.31,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,That's where they'll light the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.14,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,What's taking Kakeru so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.98,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I bet his tent got buried under the snow or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.68,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,What, he's still living in that tent in his backyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.06,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's been snowing a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.64,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I don't think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.72,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,All right, if you say so, Sacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.88,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:19.78,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.03,Glasslip-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Here's your hot orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.41,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm Fukami Touko. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.63,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Guys, introduce yourselves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.35,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.09,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm Shirosaki Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.93,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,My name's Takayama Yanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.85,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm, uh, Imi Yukinari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.14,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,What's this? You fall for Fukami-san or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.30,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Well, Yukinari falls for just about anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.70,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:04.28,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,In any case, {\i1}I'm{\i0} going to show her around Hinode Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.53,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Oh, ain't that a shame, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.74,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'm Nagamiya Sachi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.74,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:19.78,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,My dad decided to set up\Nhis workshop around here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.55,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Workshop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.18,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.46,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,He's an artisan who makes handicrafts and vases and stuff out of glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.57,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Wow, that's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.55,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's less fun than it sounds, \Nthough, because of the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.82,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,You're going to see the fireworks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.85,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,The ones they have here are really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.10,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.48,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.27,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Apparently she didn't know about tonight's fireworks display.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.19,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:48.95,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Each year, the five of us meet up at Hinode Beach Shrine to watch the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.93,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's been a long run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.62,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Ever since grade school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:59.49,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,As I recall, at first they told us to always travel in groups of three or more,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:02.13,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,and we've been stuck together ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:06.53,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Now we just meet up each year \Nwithout anyone even arranging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.50,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.93,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,You should come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.80,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,It'll be super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.11,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.21,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.49,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Right, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.25,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.70,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.57,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.21,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You're not used to this snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:22.97,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.74,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It didn't fall very often where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:32.36,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Try to keep a high center of gravity, and take small steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.08,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:40.29,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,From that balcony on the fourth floor, you can see all of Hinode Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.33,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Wanna take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.04,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I can't wait for the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.46,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You don't often hear about \Nfireworks in the winter, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.27,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.69,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I wonder what they look like amongst all the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:08.09,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I doubt you'd be able to see them anywhere but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.25,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,We're all looking forward to \Nseeing them with you, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.62,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just "Touko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.93,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko, will you be transferring in to \NHinode Beach High School as a third-year?{QC: fixed}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.78,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.01,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It must be tough, changing schools in your third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I want to major in fine arts, so I guess it's more about practical skills than study for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.74,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.64,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Are you going to follow in your father's footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.05,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't thought that far ahead yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:45.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I've never been outside this town before, so I wouldn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.94,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,but how's it feel to be in a new town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.90,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's really exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:53.12,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'd love to explore the town until the fireworks start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.12,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Shall I be your guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.21,Glasslip-Main,Touko,800,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.95,Glasslip-Main,Touko,800,0,0,,{\q2}Thanks! \NBut I think I'd prefer it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.23,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,800,0,,I see. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.83,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,800,0,,{\q2}It's not that big of a town, \Nand the people here are very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.22,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,What's this? I heard there was a new girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.93,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Look, your lack of knocking aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.09,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,when you come into a boy's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.69,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,you should give some kind of advance warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:24.06,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.70,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.94,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Obviously 'cos it's kinda risky if you don't.{LOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.02,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,So, how was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:32.19,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Eh, pretty average, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:35.41,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,No match for the fragile glasses-girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.45,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,If that's all you're here for, then kindly leave, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.06,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.45,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.16,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.06,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it just because you're feeling fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.50,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.18,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,If I hurt myself, it'd defeat the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.94,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Hurry up. I'm freezing out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.37,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Twelve seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:11.61,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, "It's important to \Nkeep a daily routine," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.65,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,That girl from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.46,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Fukami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:16.37,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.37,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,She was cute, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.04,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Man, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.76,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Jeez, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.92,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I thought he said he'd be taking the short route.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:47.75,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.87,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.92,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Same as every year with your friends at the fireworks, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.76,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.38,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.38,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Same as every year for us too, on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.09,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, and we'll be inviting Fukami-san's family too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.24,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Fukami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:07.82,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,They told us that they have two girls in middle and high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.08,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.35,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,They'll be running a glass workshop around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.21,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Isn't this wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.78,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,It turns out that they're fans of my music, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.61,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'll be meeting up with the older girl later at Hinode Beach Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.20,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Things turned out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.56,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Amongst all those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.12,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,It's her first time here in Hinode Beach, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.25,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,What if you can't find each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.16,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go and pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.76,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like they're here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:43.98,Glasslip-Main,Toukomom,0,0,0,,She sent me a text saying that she wanted to look around town before coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.19,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.70,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Would you like Touko's phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.32,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Wow, Onee-chan's been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.45,Glasslip-Main,Toukomom,0,0,0,,Yes, she has. And do you know who's just like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.66,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,She's come down with a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.91,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,But please do come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:06.87,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.45,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sacchan, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.75,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Well? Think you can make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.25,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.00,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.92,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I don't have my phone on me either.
Comment: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.57,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.32,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,My, how beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.88,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be at the neighborhood association.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.33,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.93,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Don't stay out too late, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:46.84,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.88,Glasslip-Main,Sachimom,0,0,0,,Sorry, and thank you for looking after Sachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:52.77,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Not at all! She's safe with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.32,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuki, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.73,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.00,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.84,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Hey, don't go off by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.30,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,What? You're the one being slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.30,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:26.80,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:28.93,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:30.68,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.68,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.06,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.28,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.64,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.77,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we met just a little while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.90,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they faking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.18,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.38,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:50.28,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.65,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's nothing. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.65,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.58,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.06,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,That was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.67,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.25,Glasslip-Main,Toukodad,0,0,0,,Hina, you wanted to go with Kakeru-kun too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.49,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.50,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I don't like crowds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.26,Glasslip-Main,Toukodad,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.73,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how Onee-chan's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.24,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:33.20,Glasslip-Main,Kakerudad,0,0,0,,Oh, Hina-chan, it seems you're familiar with those traditional expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.66,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Wow, they're amazing this year too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.23,Glasslip-Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.47,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.04,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.63,Glasslip-Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.16,Glasslip-Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.51,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I thought I never would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,U-Um, you can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.24,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.86,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I couldn't reach your cell either, so I was getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.52,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.16,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, it's out of battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.36,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,The others aren't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.90,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,They're over there—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.53,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But it's kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.42,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Almost as if they can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.53,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,The fireworks have started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.20,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's a little hard for me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.75,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Wanna watch from here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.08,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,The others will be waiting\Nfor us at the shrine, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.50,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Can't hurt to change it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.30,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I guess we won't be going to the shrine this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.98,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.50,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.89,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,This year can be a special exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:05.48,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,It's one of those, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.34,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,"Special moments."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.20,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Yup, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.21,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,It can be a special moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.84,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.{>drinking ramune in the winter}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.26,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Sachi, gimme a look too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.95,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm next in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:38.71,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Dude, you're so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:39.90,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.67,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Okay, fine, you can go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:44.56,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I don't think that'll count as an indirect kiss, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.00,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean, indirect...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:47.89,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:54.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Is this the world I've been seeing in my fragments of the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:55.57,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.65,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,So, are you the Kakeru-kun that I imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:03.31,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes, but I'm different from the \NKakeru from just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:08.36,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,If anything, I'm like a projection of the "me" in your real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:11.80,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,So you're just a Kakeru-kun from my imaginary world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.62,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:16.92,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What about the guys over there, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:21.13,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,They're also not real, but not in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.38,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,"Not real?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.51,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It appears that something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.14,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,They didn't meet up here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:27.78,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.94,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.33,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,And the loneliness I felt earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:51.63,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, during this fireworks display,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:56.76,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Yana-chan, Sacchan, Yuki-kun,\Nand Hiro-kun from this world can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:04.12,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must mean that I don't yet have an \Nunforgettable place I share with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.74,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.46,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:30.29,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's... It's nothing.
Comment: 0,0:22:00.92,0:23:30.88,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.07,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I think "Touko" is a beautiful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.23,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,You can tell me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:35.56,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I'm calling in your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:36.73,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Have you changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:37.86,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:40.28,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Comment: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:42.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,(ﾉಥ益ಥ）ﾉ ┻━┻　/（。□。ハNooo, my firstborn!
