Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.35,0:22:15.06,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and bring me back to life again.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.42,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Hearts are fragile like glass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.12,0:22:32.30,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and shatter into pieces when they're broken.
